title: 841. Dolphins Violations + Draft of Last Place Teams
itunes:title: 841. Dolphins Violations + Draft of Last Place Teams
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, DJ emphasizes his excitement for the Padres landing Juan Soto. Then, the pair react to the news of the Dolphins being stripped of draft picks and given other fines for violating the integrity of the game. Next, Bucky gives his takeaways from his time at Jaguars training camp. For the rest of the show, the duo does a draft of the last place teams from every division to determine which will be the most improved this season.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
